    <string name="guide_content">👉 Recruit Pets: Go to the Recruitment office to find new companions. Each pet has unique stats based on their role (Pilot, Medic,...).\n👉 Train &amp; Simulate: Use the Training Room to improve your pet\'s skills and prepare them for real cosmic threats.\n👉 Manage Quarters: Check your pet list in the Quarters to monitor their energy and specialization.\n👉 Mission Control: Assign your best pets to missions. Success depends on the right match of skills!.\n👉 Save the Galaxy: Rescue pets and keep your crew happy! 🐾</string>
